Edit 1: Here is the output, I think the input is correct PS C:\Users\user> openssl version OpenSSL 0.9.8y 5 Feb 2013 PS C:\Users\user> openssl dgst -sha1 -out C:\test.hash -hmac "0123456789ABCDEFFEDCBA9876543210" C:\alpha2.pdf PS C:\Users\user> cat c:\test.hash 0123456789ABCDEFFEDCBA987654321034f051d2 (stdin)= 21ba283eae7a6a99b6e7e8d9a6dc1ff6f5d89a55 PS C:\Users\user> cat c:\alpha2.hash 0123456789ABCDEFFEDCBA98765432101c100af2 (stdin)= a4e99a7d8e9bef1518c21f89794716829695527draw A: It looks like you are including 0123456789ABCDEFFEDCBA9876543210 in your input, and then here: $bObstructionString = 0x01020304050607080910111213141516.ToByteArray() You are filling a 16-byte buffer with the 20 ASN.1 octets 0x01 0x02 ... 0x16. Those cannot be the same, assuming the 20-octet message you're reference came before this process. It is important that you also include the last octet of your 20-octet text json data (so include 21 octets in all), as recommended in that article.

## 方法

### 重载

IE以外浏览器（如Chrome27+）支持通过`ResizeObserver`实现重载。IE等不支持`ResizeObserver`的浏览器使用初始化周期钩子重载。

### 换主题

通过按钮切换主题。在切换时，原有主题的style不会立即移除，只是通过css的`all`属性移除了该主题的css代码。这样保证了切换主题完成前，由于style覆盖仍保持旧主题样式。
